{"word":"ἀνηκουστέω","slug":"ἀνηκουστέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνηκουστέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἀνήκουστος'><el>ἀνήκουστος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to be unwilling to hear, to disobey</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/>"}]}